snippet.title: Plotting (Commodore 64) - Unreleased puzzler
snippet.description:
Plotting was due for release on C64 cartridge from Ocean in 1990. Believed to be cancelled after being leaked onto the cracking scene before launch. Hopefully the coder will soon help solve the mystery of what happened.

https://www.gamesthatwerent.com/gtw64/plotting/
